01:01:07.630 --> 01:01:09.965
Note, the feathers
for aerodynamics,

01:01:09.999 --> 01:01:11.568
the sparkly color
to dazzle the enemy,

01:01:11.601 --> 01:01:13.603
the boots purely decorative.

01:01:13.636 --> 01:01:15.105
And this,

01:01:15.138 --> 01:01:18.441
