01:04:29.532 --> 01:04:33.336
It'd just be a sympathy kiss,
which doesn't count.

01:04:35.338 --> 01:04:37.106
You're not a Nazi.

01:04:37.140 --> 01:04:38.641
Uh, I'm massively
into swastikas,

01:04:38.674 --> 01:04:40.743
